  {
    "id": "f_csv_df1c2c01ea",
    "slug": "to-come-devotedly-into-the-depths-of-a-subject-your-respect-for-it-increasing-i",
    "texto": "To come devotedly into the depths of a subject, your respect for it increasing in every step and your whole heart weakening apart with shame upon yourself in your dealing with it : To know at length better and better and at length into the bottom of your soul your unworthiness of it : Let me hope in any case that it is something to have begun to learn.",
